Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/TC/TC_01 - To verify that opty creation for the new customer
bool_Opportunity && bool_Account && bool_Customer && bool_Influencer && bool_FollowUp == false

Description:
STEP-01 : Click on + icon

Expected_Result : The pop up should appear and below 4 option should be listed
1. Opportunity
2. Customer
3. Account
4. Influencer

STEP-02 : The user successfully  landed on the Add Opportunity screen with the below options-:
1. Add Contact
2. Search bar for existing contact search
STEP-03 : The user successfully enters the name and respective name should be visible

STEP-04 : Enter all the details and select check box of also an influencer and click on Next
Expected_Result : The popup successfully appears to select the contact

STEP-06 : Click on Proceed

Expected_Result : The user clicks on proceed and successfully land on the vehicle information page

STEP-07 : Select the Product line and model

Expected_Result : The user should be able to select the product line and model option

Actual_Result : The user selects the product line option and model option

STEP-08 : Select the vehicle application and body type

Expected_Result : The user should be land on the vehicle application and body type and should land on the select quantity

Actual_Result : The user landed on the vehicle application and body type and  landed on the select quantity

STEP-08 : Select the vehicle application and body type

Expected_Result : The user should be land on the vehicle application and body type and should land on the select quantity

Actual_Result : The user landed on the vehicle application and body type and  landed on the select quantity

STEP-09 : Enter the quantity and click on Next

Expected_Result : The user should be able to add the quantity and by clicking on Next the user should land on the select purchase month screen

Actual_Result : The user added the quantity and by clicking on Next the user  landed on the select purchase month screen

STEP-10 : Select the source of contact

Expected_Result : The user should be able to select the contact and should landed on the customer interest option

Actual_Result : The user selects the contact and landed on the customer interest page

STEP-11 : Select the customer interest option

Expected_Result : The user should able to select the customer interest option and the exchange type option should be visible to the user

Actual_Result : The user selects the customer interest option and on the exchange type screen should appear

STEP-12 : Enter the quantity and Make and click on Next

Expected_Result : The user should be land on the review opty screen

Actual_Result : The user landed on the review opty screen
